high_descs: walk forwards a bit to the garbage bin on your left
grab the apple out of the garbage bin
turn left and walk over to the kitchen stove at the near end of the right side of the room, then look up at the microwave above the stove
place the apple inside of the microwave, cook it, then take it back out
turn left and walk over to the fridge on the right side of the room, but then turn left to walk over to the garbage bin again up ahead on the floor
place the apple inside of the garbage bin
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved apple inside the garbage bin

high_descs: Turn left and go to the front of the trash can.
Pick up the apple on the right in the trash can.
Turn left and then go right to the stove.
Put the apple in the microwave above the stove, cook the apple and then take it out.
Turn left, go to the fridge and turn left again and go to the trash can.
Put the cooked apple in the trash can next to the other apple.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple in the trash can.

high_descs: Move around the trash can in front of you, face the trash can by the end of the island.
Pick up the apple on the right side of the trash can.
Turn left, go to the fridge, turn right, go to the stove, turn left and bring the apple to the microwave over the stove.
Heat the apple in the microwave over the stove.
Take the heated apple from the microwave, head back around the island to the left, face the trash can.
Put the apple in the right side of the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple in the trash can.
